Someone moves by jumping 0.7-1.5 m. The width of the footsteps is 10x10 cm. On an area of about 30x30 meters, I found 6 holes as on last 3 photos. All footsteps are in the same style as in the 1st photo. The last photo shows the tag of a large animal next to one of the holes

It looks very much like it is the same species or instance as here, where the footprint is better visible:
https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/144144427
But now new details.
1. Can do 2.5 m long run-up jumps (photo 4)
2. Walks with sharp angles (photo 5)
3. Sometimes returns in his tracks, sometimes not (photo 6)
4. Makes small marks with urine. One was found next to a hole, apparently of this species (photo 7):
https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/144411345
5. Digs the ground (photos 8, 9)

В городке где мы живём, в двух разных квартирах в разные годы я иногда видел такие существа. Они живут в ванных комнатах (никогда не видел в других помещениях) и всегда прячутся от людей. Увидеть их можно только зайдя в ванную ночью или если оно попало в сосуд-ловушку, из которого не может выбраться (в ванную, например)

In the town we live, in two different apartments in different years, I sometimes saw such creatures. They live in bathrooms (never seen in other rooms) and are always hiding from people. You can only see them by going into the bathroom at night or if it has fallen into a "trap" container from which it cannot get out (into the bathtub, for example)
